				<td colspan="2"><span><i>~~This is going to turn into a flame war if we're not careful. There's another thread on this board that's pretty much dominated by an argument over whether or not soloing IS a good learning experience. There's a lot of bards who believe that if you solo too much you'll miss a lot of learning experiences that come from grouping. 
