<br />

<br />
Ok, so, next question is this...How do you know which instrument to buy, when to use it and when not to use it, and whats the best that you can recommend for my level at decent price. I don't want to twink this character out, I am trying to do this as if it was my first character ever played, lol, which may sound silly, but that is what I am trying. So, here I am, a level 12 bard, almost 13, with about 30 plat in the bank so far. What would be the best recommendations for purchasing an instrument and why that particular one? 
<br />
</span></td>
