				<td colspan="2"><span><a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=8687">Combine lute</a>: Found in Katta, cost about 60pp.
<br />

<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=8682">Combine Hand Drum</a> about 20pp.
<br />

<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=8683">Combine Wooden Flute</a> about 20pp.
<br />

<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=8683">Combine Horn</a> about 60pp.
<br />

<br />
All links are to Allakhazam.com  Prices are per posts there.
<br />
Not cheep, but not overly expensive, and all are off hand so swapping them out is easy enough.
<br />

<br />
Start with the lute, I'd say, and get a drum asap.  You will need the wind instrument for invis.
<br />

<br />
Hope this helps a little.
<br />

<br />
Oh, and look over to the left, where it says <a target="_new" href="http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/items/instruments.aspx">instruments</a>.  You can find every instrument with mods and more.  Very useful.</span></td>
